title: JAUMO: Dating, Flirt & Friends

creator: Joyride GmbH
descriptionHtml:
MEET NEW PEOPLE LIVE, CHAT & FIND FRIENDS! 💕
Looking for a free dating app that really works? There is a reason Jaumo has been downloaded over 50,000,000 times: We’re a free dating & a social app in one. With Jaumo, you can make real connections with real people in a real life. Chat with local singles, find friends and build an authentic relationship.

MEET SINGLES IN A LIVE VOICE CHAT 💗🎤👩‍🦰👨‍🦱

Attend our 24/7 live, public voice chat, designed to help you meet new friends and enrich your social life. Join Live audio rooms and be part of funny talks and genuine conversations. Discover those conversations you’d skip sleep for. Jaumo is a social community where we scroll less and connect more. Want to be the life of the party? Become a room host, create your own event, go live** and lead those talks & conversations with other singles!

TRUST US: YOUR NEW MATCH IS JUST ONE DOWNLOAD AWAY! ⬇️
With Jaumo we provide a totally new dating experience. We think that meeting new people is easier online, whilst actual dating and sharing experiences together works better offline. With us you can meet local new people with easy zapping & voice messages, chat & flirt a little and even play an online trivia game with your friends and then meet them in real life on our offline events! Date, find new friends, love and connect with people nearby. Meeting new people in real life has never been easier!

THE SAFE DATING & SOCIAL APP EXPERIENCE.🕵🏿
The Jaumo experience has been designed to help you find your people by interests and helps you flirt and socialise in a small network of friends. Also, we make your safety our priority through live video verification. Verify your profile in minutes with a simple process that ensures that our community is full of real life human beings!We use powerful privacy and anti-scam settings and only show you verified singles that are relevant to your interests. 🥰

SCROLL LESS & STREAM MORE. JAUMO IS A VOICE STREAMING PLATFORM - FOR FREE! 🎤

That’s right, Jaumo isn´t just a free dating app. It is also a live streaming & socialising platform, where you can find friends and connect with people using just your voice! Meet local singles online in a group chat, flirt, find love or just make new friends without any payment involved. Sign-up is simple and easy: join over 50 million users and start chatting with your perfect match today. We help you connect with a diverse, growing community close to your place - for free! You can also access the very best Jaumo has to offer with an upgrade to VIP membership.

GET THE MOST OUT OF JAUMO WITH VIP!


☑️ See who already liked you. Match with other singles instantly!
☑️ Get unlimited likes. Like as many singles as you want!
☑️ No more ads. Ever!
☑️ Chat with new local singles before everyone else!
☑️ Get unlimited filters! Find your match by interests - define location, age, habits, hobbies and more!

A FUN WAY OF DATING! 🎉
Finding love, building a relationship and making friends should be fun! Our dating app’s detailed profiles allow you to find like-minded people, chat about common interests in a voice chat, flirt using voice messages and even play Trivia together. 🕹️ With Jaumo, you can be part of an open-minded and accepting online dating experience. Join our community now!

👉FOLLOW US AND STAY UPDATED:
[https://instagram.com/jaumo](https://instagram.com/jaumo)[https://facebook.com/jaumo](https://facebook.com/jaumo)
For more information, read our Privacy Policy and Terms of Use: [https://jaumo.com/privacy](https://jaumo.com/privacy) [https://jaumo.com/terms](https://jaumo.com/terms) 📲

CHAT, MEET NEW PEOPLE LIVE & FIND FRIENDS! 💕
Find love and friends with your passions! Connect with new people who share your hobbies and interests using the top-rated dating app.

Do you want to make new friends? Are you looking for a free dating app that works? There's a reason Jaumo has been downloaded over 50 million times! We're a free dating and social app not just for singles designed to help you meet new friends and enrich your social life. With Jaumo, you can make real connections with real people. Chat with local singles, find friends, meet LGBTQ+ people, and build authentic relationships.

A WORLD OF NEW FRIENDS: MEET NEW PEOPLE IN COMMUNITIES! 👩‍🦰👨‍🦱


Discover chat conversations you'd skip sleep for. Jaumo communities are interest groups that connect like-minded people. Through communities, you can chat, make new friends, become part of themed groups, and share your passions or interests with new friends across the country! Discover communities like: "LGBTQ+", "Fitness Lovers", "Friends with Benefits", "Big is Beautiful," and many more to find new people who are into the same things as you. Chat inside the communities and join chats with people nearby or worldwide. Find matches, and enjoy the excitement of flirting, meeting new people, or finding love. Find the perfect community for you, expand your social circle, and connect with people who truly understand you.

YOUR NEW MATCH IS WAITING! ⭐️


At Jaumo, we provide a new dating and social experience. Through communities, you can meet people passionate about the same topics as you. By writing messages in the community chat or by sending a message to someone you like, you can get in touch with new people and meet them in real life at our user-run community meet-ups. If you're looking for a date, you can use the match game to meet local singles, send text & voice messages, chat & flirt a little, and then meet them in real life when you feel confident and safe. Date, find new friends, love, and connect with people nearby. Meeting new people in real life has never been easier! 🧡

🔒 We prioritize your safety with a quick video verification process to ensure only real humans join our platform. It maintains integrity and gives peace of mind to members. 🥰

JAUMO IS A FREE CHAT & DATING APP!


Meet local singles online in chats, flirt, find love, or make new friends without payment. Sign-up is simple and easy: join over 50 million singles and start chatting with your perfect match today. Jaumo is a free app, but you can access the very best Jaumo offers with an upgrade to our premium membership.

With our Premium membership, you get incredible benefits such as instantly seeing who has liked you, unlimited likes to express your interest in other singles or friends, ad-free browsing, priority chat with new local singles, and unlimited filters to find your perfect match.

✅ See who already liked you and match with other singles instantly
✅ Get access to all premium communities
✅ Get unlimited likes: Like as many singles as you want
✅ Chat with new local singles before everyone else
✅ Unlimited filters: Find your match by interests, hobbies, and more
✅ Enjoy an ad-free experience

A FUN WAY OF DATING & MAKING FRIENDS! 🎉


Making friends, finding love, or building a relationship should be fun! Our social and dating app's detailed profiles allow you to find like-minded people, chat about common interests in a voice chat, flirt using voice messages, join communities, and even organize meet-ups and events together. 🥳 With Jaumo, you can be part of an open-minded and accepting online dating and online friendship experience. Join now!
